         MACRO                                                                  
&L       VCALL &NAME,&ALTNAME                                                   
*JOIN                                                                           
&L       L     EPAR,=V(&NAME)                                                   
         AIF   ('&ALTNAME' EQ '').BAL                                           
         LTR   EPAR,EPAR                                                        
         AIF   ('&ALTNAME' EQ '*').SKIPZ                                        
         BZ    &ALTNAME                                                         
.BAL     BASR  RAR,EPAR                                                         
         MEXIT                                                                  
.SKIPZ   BZ    *+6                                                              
         AGO   .BAL                                                             
         MEND                                                                   
